name: Massimo Bottura
description: The Italian National Chefs' Team (NIC) on Friday won the senior category of the Global Chef Challenge in Dubai beating Sweden and Singapore. Italy also got two second places: in the junior category, with young chef Giorgia Ceccato, and the pastry category, with Antonio Dell'Oro and Luca Bnà.
